Summary:	PC/SC driver for REINER SCT cyberjack USB chip card reader
Version:	3.99.5final.SP13
%global version_prefix %(c=%{version}; echo ${c:0:6})
%global version_suffix %(c=%{version}; echo ${c:12:4})
